  "title": "Burden Of Time",
  "description": "Breathe life into your world as you watch it age and change",
  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/unionlib\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://tiny.one/unionlib\" alt=\"UnionLib\" width=\"177\" height=\"25\" /></a>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Minecraft-1.16.x-0967fc?labelColor=537DB5&amp;style=flat-square\" alt=\"Minecraft Version\" width=\"133\" height=\"25\" />&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/linkout?remoteUrl=https%253a%252f%252ffiles.minecraftforge.net%252fnet%252fminecraftforge%252fforge%252findex_1.16.5.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Loader-Forge-0967fc?labelColor=537DB5&amp;style=flat-square&amp;logo=curseforge\" alt=\"Forge\" width=\"131\" height=\"25\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/8MXShqa\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/648116022020145203?label=&amp;color=014980&amp;labelColor=537DB5&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=Discord&amp;logoColor=DDE4EF&amp;link=https://discord.gg/8MXShqa\" alt=\"Stereowalkers Discord\" width=\"121\" height=\"25\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/Stereowalker\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?label=&amp;color=014980&amp;labelColor=537DB5&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=Patreon&amp;logoColor=DDE4EF&amp;url=https://shieldsio-patreon.vercel.app/api/?username=stereowalker&amp;type=patrons\" alt=\"Patreon\" width=\"116\" height=\"25\" /></a></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'courier new', courier, monospace; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>ABOUT</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'courier new', courier, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Burden Of Time is a mod that allows your world to age without input from the player.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'courier new', courier, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'courier new', courier, monospace; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>FEATURES</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'courier new', courier, monospace; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Social Trails (Desire Paths) -&nbsp;</strong>This adds social trails (desire paths) to your world. Any mob crossing a grassy area will, after a period of time, cause the ground to start eroding. The order in which the ground changes are Grass Block &gt; Dirt &gt; Coarse Dirt &gt; Grass Path</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'courier new', courier, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'courier new', courier, monospace; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Mossing -&nbsp;</strong>Over a period of time, certain blocks that have moss variants will begin to grow moss on them. This effect can be sped up in the config or by ramping up the random tick speed of your world.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'courier new', courier, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'courier new', courier, monospace; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Fluid Erosion -&nbsp;</strong>Water and lava will have certain effects on blocks. Flowing water will over time crack certain blocks that have cracked variants and lava, both still and flowing will bake blocks that can be baked</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'courier new', courier, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'courier new', courier, monospace; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>MODPACK USAGE</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'courier new', courier, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">You're free to add this mod in your modpack, as long as you credit where credit is due</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'courier new', courier, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'courier new', courier, monospace; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>CREDITS<br /></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'courier new', courier, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">I'd like to give my thanks to all my patrons on Patreon. It's thanks to their support that I still actively make these mods, so here they are:</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: 'courier new', courier, monospace; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Diamond</strong>&nbsp;👉 Mr_Jakob99,&nbsp;Kuechenbulle, Blue, Kudos</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1081639899188449420/1081661429586862160/Stereowalker.png\" width=\"873\" height=\"395\" /></p>",
